### 8.3 Auction Management

| Action | Description | Condition |
|---|---|---|
| **View All Auctions** | See all listed auctions with status, bids, current price | Always available |
| **Edit Auction** | Update title, description, images, category, dates, price, security % | Only before auction ends |
| **Close Auction Early** | Manually end an active auction | Seller or Admin only |
| **View Top 5 Bidders** | See ranked bidders with details after completion | Completed auctions |
| **Send Payment Reminder** | Email the winner to complete payment | Winner hasn't paid |
| **Mark as Paid (Cash)** | Manually update payment status for offline payment | Winner paying in cash |
| **Activate Second-Chance** | Email top 4 runner-ups if winner defaults | Winner hasn't paid |
| **Accept/Reject Offers** | Review second-chance offers from runner-ups | Second-chance is open |
| **Date Filtering** | Filter auctions by date range (from/to) | Always available |

### 8.4 Post-Auction Detail View

When an auction completes, the seller sees:
- **Winner information**: Name, email, phone, full shipping address
- **Top 5 bidders**: Ranked list with bid amounts, deposit amounts, bid counts
- **Payment status**: Pending / Paid
- **Remaining amount**: Winner's winning bid minus their locked security deposit
- **Action buttons**: Send Reminder, Mark as Paid, Activate Second-Chance

