### 10.1 Complete Auction Lifecycle

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Creation["1’ĖÅŌāŻ Creation Phase"]
        S1["Seller creates auction"]
        S2["Sets title, description,<br/>images, prices, dates"]
        S3["Status: Active"]
        S1 --> S2 --> S3
    end
    
    subgraph Bidding["2’ĖÅŌāŻ Bidding Phase"]
        B1["Buyers browse & place bids"]
        B2["Security deposits locked"]
        B3["Real-time WebSocket updates"]
        B4["Sniper protection triggers<br/>if bid in last 10 min"]
        B1 --> B2 --> B3 --> B4
    end
    
    subgraph Completion["3’ĖÅŌāŻ Completion Phase"]
        C1["Auction end date reached<br/>OR Seller/Admin force-close"]
        C2["Highest bidder = Winner"]
        C3["Winner's deposit ŌåÆ Payment"]
        C4["Losers' deposits ŌåÆ Refunded"]
        C5["Status: Completed"]
        C1 --> C2 --> C3 --> C4 --> C5
    end
    
    subgraph Payment["4’ĖÅŌāŻ Payment Phase"]
        P1["Winner views remaining amount"]
        P2["Enters shipping address"]
        P3["Pays via Razorpay OR<br/>Seller marks cash payment"]
        P4["Payment verified & confirmed"]
        P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4
    end
    
    subgraph Delivery["5’ĖÅŌāŻ Delivery Phase"]
        D1["Seller sees winner's<br/>address & phone"]
        D2["Seller ships item"]
        D3["Transaction complete Ō£ģ"]
        D1 --> D2 --> D3
    end
    
    subgraph SecondChance["6’ĖÅŌāŻ Second-Chance (if winner defaults)"]
        SC1["Seller activates<br/>second-chance"]
        SC2["Top 4 runner-ups notified"]
        SC3["Runner-ups submit offers<br/>(┬▒5% of winning bid)"]
        SC4["Seller accepts best offer"]
        SC1 --> SC2 --> SC3 --> SC4
    end
    
    Creation --> Bidding --> Completion --> Payment --> Delivery
    Payment -.->|Winner defaults| SecondChance
```

