### 10.3 Wallet Integrity Verification Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Any wallet mutation requested"] --> B["Load user from DB"]
    B --> C["assertWalletIntegrity(user)"]
    C --> D{"walletHash exists?"}
    D -->|No (Legacy user)| E["Allow ŌĆö will sign on mutation"]
    D -->|Yes| F["Recompute HMAC:<br/>HMAC-SHA256(userId|balance|locked)"]
    F --> G{"Computed hash =<br/>Stored hash?"}
    G -->|Yes Ō£ģ| H["Integrity verified"]
    G -->|No ŌØī| I["­¤Ü© SECURITY ALERT<br/>Balance may be tampered"]
    I --> J["Operation blocked<br/>Contact support"]
    H --> K["Perform wallet mutation"]
    K --> L["resignWallet(user)<br/>Compute new HMAC"]
    L --> M["Save user with new hash"]
    E --> K
```

### 10.4 Profanity Filtering Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["User submits content<br/>(title, description, address)"] --> B["Server receives input"]
    B --> C["containsProfanity(text)"]
    C --> D["Generate 4 normalized versions:"]
    D --> D1["v1: Remove separators"]
    D --> D2["v2: Strip non-alphanumeric"]
    D --> D3["v3: De-obfuscate l33tspeak"]
    D --> D4["v4: Decode special chars"]
    D1 --> E["Check against 100+ banned words<br/>(English + Hindi)"]
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    D4 --> E
    E --> F{"Match found?"}
    F -->|Yes| G["ŌØī Reject with error:<br/>'Contains inappropriate language'"]
    F -->|No| H["Ō£ģ Content accepted"]
```

