## 11. Security & Integrity Mechanisms

### 11.1 Wallet Security (HMAC-SHA256)

| Mechanism | Details |
|---|---|
| **Algorithm** | HMAC-SHA256 |
| **Secret** | `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` (never exposed to client) |
| **Payload Format** | `userId|walletBalance|lockedBalance` |
| **Verification** | `crypto.timingSafeEqual()` to prevent timing attacks |
| **When Verified** | Before EVERY wallet mutation (top-up, withdrawal, bid deposit, refund) |
| **When Re-signed** | After EVERY wallet mutation, before `user.save()` |

### 11.2 Server-Side Validation

| Check | Details |
|---|---|
| **Amount Validation** | All amounts validated server-side: `typeof === 'number'`, `Number.isFinite()`, range checks |
| **Max Top-up Cap** | Single top-up capped at Ōé╣5,00,000 |
| **Min Withdrawal** | Minimum withdrawal amount: Ōé╣100 |
| **IFSC Validation** | Regex: `^[A-Z]{4}0[A-Z0-9]{6}$` |
| **Account Number** | Regex: `^\d{9,18}$` |
| **Balance from DB** | All balance checks use database values, NEVER client-provided values |
| **Self-Bidding Prevention** | Sellers cannot bid on their own auctions |
| **Self-Deletion Prevention** | Admins cannot delete their own account |

### 11.3 Anti-Sniper Protection

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Trigger Condition** | Bid placed with Ōēż 10 minutes remaining |
| **Action** | Auction end date extended by 1 hour |
| **Notification** | Email sent to top 10 bidders about the extension |
| **Purpose** | Prevents last-second sniping and ensures fair competition |

### 11.4 Content Safety

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Profanity Filter** | 100+ banned words (English + Hindi) |
| **L33tspeak Detection** | Character substitution map (@ ŌåÆ a, ! ŌåÆ i, $ ŌåÆ s, etc.) |
| **Multi-version Check** | 4 normalized text versions checked against word list |
| **Wildcard Patterns** | Catches `f**k`, `s**t`, `b**ch` type obfuscations |
| **Applied To** | Auction titles, descriptions, shipping addresses |

### 11.5 Authentication Security

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Session Strategy** | JWT (stateless) |
| **OAuth Provider** | Google (verified accounts only) |
| **OTP Authentication** | Email-based one-time password |
| **Session Update** | JWT refresh on profile/role changes |
| **Route Protection** | Server-side session validation on all API routes |

