## 14. Real-Time Communication

### 14.1 WebSocket Architecture

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Server** | Socket.IO (on custom HTTP server) | Broadcast auction events |
| **Client** | socket.io-client | Receive real-time updates |
| **Rooms** | Per-auction rooms (`itemId`) | Scope updates to auction viewers |

### 14.2 Events

| Event | Direction | Data | Trigger |
|---|---|---|---|
| `joinRoom` | Client ŌåÆ Server | `itemId` | User opens auction detail page |
| `leaveRoom` | Client ŌåÆ Server | `itemId` | User leaves auction page |
| `bidUpdated` | Server ŌåÆ Clients | `{ itemId, newPrice, endDate, highestBidderId, bidCount }` | New bid placed |
| `auctionCompleted` | Server ŌåÆ Clients | `{ itemId, winnerId, finalPrice }` | Auction marked complete |

