## 16. Payment Integration

### 16.1 Razorpay Integration

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Gateway** | Razorpay (Indian payments) |
| **Currency** | INR (Ōé╣) |
| **Flow** | Create Order ŌåÆ Client-side checkout ŌåÆ Server-side verification |
| **Signature Verification** | HMAC-SHA256 using `RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET` |
| **Receipt Format** | `rb_{auctionId_last8}_{timestamp_base36}` |

### 16.2 Payment Calculation

```
Winning Amount = Item.finalAmount || Item.currentPrice
Locked Deposit = Sum of all user's bids' lockedDeposit on this auction
Remaining Amount = max(0, Winning Amount ŌłÆ Locked Deposit)
```

### 16.3 Payment Methods

| Method | Flow |
|---|---|
| **Online (Razorpay)** | Winner pays remaining amount via Razorpay ŌåÆ Signature verified ŌåÆ Status: paid |
| **Cash** | Winner pays seller in cash ŌåÆ Seller clicks "Mark as Paid" ŌåÆ Status: paid |
| **Bank Transfer** | (Supported in schema, manual process) |

